 templates'=>'E-postmallar','Data protection'=>'Dataskydd','Payments'=>'Betalningar','Maps'=>'Kartor','Other'=>'ûvrigt','The EME SEO permalink settings are conflicting with itself (the permalink prefix setting for either events, locations or categories contains a value that is not unique). Please resolve the conflict by changing your EME SEO permalink settings.'=>'EME:s SEO-permalûÊnksinstûÊllningar stûËr i konflikt med sig sjûÊlva (permalûÊnkprefixinstûÊllningen fûÑr evenemang, platser eller kategorier innehûËller ett vûÊrde som inte ûÊr unikt). VûÊnligen lûÑser konflikten genom att ûÊndra EME:s SEO-permalûÊnksinstûÊllningar.','The EME SEO permalink settings are conflicting with an existing page (the permalink setting for either events, locations or categories is identical with the permalink of another WordPress page). This might cause problems rendering either events or that page. Please resolve the conflict by either changing your EME SEO permalink settings or the permalink of the conflicting page.'=>'EME:s SEO-permalûÊnksinstûÊllningar stûËr i konflikt med en befintlig sida (permalûÊnkinstûÊllningen fûÑr evenemang, platser eller kategorier ûÊr identisk med permalûÊnken fûÑr en annan WordPress-sida). Detta kan orsaka problem vid rendering av antingen evenemang eller den sidan. VûÊnligen lûÑser konflikten genom att antingen ûÊndra EME:s SEO-permalûÊnksinstûÊllningar eller permalûÊnken fûÑr den konfliktskapande sidan.','Please also check <a href=\'%s\'>your profile</a> for some per-user EME settings.'=>'VûÊnligen kolla in <a href=\'%s\'>din profil</a> fûÑr EME-instûÊllningar per anvûÊndare.','General options'=>'AllmûÊnna instûÊllningar','Use dropdown for locations?'=>'AnvûÊnd rullgardin fûÑr platser?','Select yes to select the location from a drop-down menu; location selection will be faster, but you will lose the ability to insert locations with events.'=>'VûÊlj ja fûÑr att vûÊlja platsen frûËn en rullgardinsmeny; platsvalen blir snabbare, men du fûÑrlorar mûÑjligheten att infoga platser med evenemang.','When the qtranslate plugin is installed and activated, this setting will be ignored and always considered \'Yes\'.'=>'Om qtranslate-tillûÊgget ûÊr installerat och aktiverat kommer denna instûÊllning att ignoreras och alltid betraktas som ãJaã.','Add events and locations to WP link search function?'=>'LûÊgg till event och platser i WP lûÊnksûÑkningsfunktionen?','If selected, events and locations will be shown in the link search when creating links in the WordPress editor.'=>'Om markerad kommer evenemang och platser att visas i lûÊnksûÑkningen nûÊr lûÊnkar skapas i WordPress-redigeraren.','Use RSVP?'=>'AnvûÊnd OSA?','Select yes to enable the RSVP feature so people can register for an event and book seats.'=>'VûÊlj Ja fûÑr att aktivera OSA-funktionen sûË att personer kan registrera sig till event och boka platser.','Use tasks?'=>'AnvûÊnd uppgifter?','Select yes to enable the Tasks feature so people can sign up for event tasks (volunteer management).'=>'VûÊlj ja fûÑr att aktivera uppgiftsfunktionen sûË att personer kan registrera sig fûÑr evenemangsuppgifter (volontûÊrhantering).','Use categories?'=>'AnvûÊnd kategorier?','Select yes to enable the category features.'=>'VûÊlj Ja fûÑr att aktivera kategorifunktionen.','Use attributes?'=>'AnvûÊnd attribut?','Select yes to enable the attributes feature.'=>'VûÊlj Ja fûÑr att aktivera attributfunktionen.','Enable Maps?'=>'Aktivera kartor?','Check this option to be able to show a map of the event or location using #_MAP or the available shortcodes.'=>'VûÊlj Ja fûÑr att kunna visa en karta fûÑr eventet eller platsen med #_MAP eller tillgûÊngliga kortkoder.','Always include JS in header?'=>'Inkludera alltid JS i headern?','Some themes are badly designed and can have issues showing the map or advancing in the calendar. If so, try activating this option which will cause the javascript to always be included in the header of every page (off by default).'=>'Vissa teman ûÊr dûËligt designa