, ...). Use 0 for no limit.'=>'Antal event att visa i en lista om ingen specifik grûÊns anges (anvûÊnds i kortkoden eme_events. RSS-flûÑde, platshûËllarna #_NEXTEVENTS och #_PASTEVENTS, ãÎ). Ange 0 fûÑr ingen grûÊns.','Initial status for a new event'=>'Initial status fûÑr ett nytt event','URL to redirect private events to'=>'URL att omdirigera private event till','When a person that is not logged-in wants to look at a private event, that person is redirected to the WordPress login page. If you want to redirect to another url, enter it here. The permalink of the current visited page will be added to the mentioned url query string with a parameter called "redirect".'=>'NûÊr en person som inte ûÊr inloggad vill se ett privat evenemang, omdirigeras personen till WordPress-inloggningssidan. Om du vill omdirigera till en annan URL, ange den hûÊr. PermûÊnken fûÑr den aktuella sidan lûÊggs till i den angivna URL:ens frûËgestrûÊng med en parameter som heter "redirect".','Events format'=>'Format fûÑr event','Default event list format header'=>'Standard sidhuvudformat fûÑr eventlistor','This content will appear just above your code for the default event list format. If you leave this empty, the value <code>%s</code> will be used.'=>'Detta innehûËll visas precis ovanfûÑr din kod fûÑr standardformatet fûÑr eventlistan. Om du lûÊmnar detta blankt, kommer vûÊrdet <code>%s</code> att anvûÊndas.','Default categories event list format header'=>'Standard sidhuvudformat fûÑr eventkategorilista','This content will appear just above your code for the event list format when showing events for a specific category. If you leave this empty, the value <code>%s</code> will be used.'=>'Detta innehûËll visas precis ovanfûÑr din kod fûÑr standardformatet fûÑr eventkategorilistan nûÊr du visar event av en viss kategori. Om du lûÊmnar detta blankt, kommer vûÊrdet <code>%s</code> att anvûÊndas.','Default event list format'=>'Standardformat fûÑr eventlista','The format of any events in a list.'=>'Format fûÑr event i en lista.','Default event list format footer'=>'Fottext fûÑr standardformat fûÑr eventlista ','This content will appear just below your code for the default event list format. If you leave this empty, the value <code>%s</code> will be used.'=>'Detta innehûËll visas precis under din kod fûÑr standardformatet fûÑr eventlistan. Om du lûÊmnar detta blankt, kommer vûÊrdet <code>%s</code> att anvûÊndas.','Default categories event list format footer'=>'Fottext fûÑr standardformat fûÑr eventkategorilista ','This content will appear just below your code for the default event list format when showing events for a specific category. If you leave this empty, the value <code>%s</code> will be used.'=>'Detta innehûËll visas precis under din kod fûÑr standardformatet fûÑr eventkategorilistan nûÊr du visar event av en viss kategori. Om du lûÊmnar detta blankt, kommer vûÊrdet <code>%s</code> att anvûÊndas.','Single event page title format'=>'Rubrikformat fûÑr enstaka event','Single event html title format'=>'Html rubrikformat fûÑr enstaka event',' The default is: '=>'Standard ûÊr:','Default single event format'=>'Standardformat fûÑr enstaka event','The format of a single event page.<br>Follow the previous formatting instructions. <br>Use <code>#_MAP</code> to insert a map.<br>Use <code>#_CONTACTNAME</code>, <code>#_CONTACTEMAIL</code>, <code>#_CONTACTPHONE</code> to insert respectively the name, email address and phone number of the designated contact person. <br>Use <code>#_ADDBOOKINGFORM</code> to insert a form to allow the user to respond to your events booking one or more seats (RSVP).<br> Use <code>#_REMOVEBOOKINGFORM</code> to insert a form where users, inserting their name and email address, can remove their bookings.'=>'Formatet fûÑr en enskild evenemangssida.<br>FûÑlj de fûÑregûËende formateringsinstruktionerna. <br>AnvûÊnd <code>#_MAP</code> fûÑr att infoga en karta.<br>AnvûÊnd <code>#_CONTACTNAME</code>, <code>#_CONTACTEMAIL</code>, <code>#_CONTACTPHONE</code> fûÑr att infoga respektive namn, e-postadress och telefonnummer fûÑr den utsedda kontaktpersonen. <br>AnvûÊnd <code>#_ADDBOOKINGFORM</code> fûÑr att infoga ett formulûÊr som tillûËter anvûÊndaren att boka en eller flera platser fûÑr dina evenemang (OSA).<br> AnvûÊnd <code>#_REMOVEBOOKINGFORM</code> fûÑr att infoga ett formulûÊr dûÊr anvûÊndare, genom att ange sitt namn och e-postadress, kan ta bort sina bokningar.','<br>Use <code>#_ADDBOOKINGFORM_IF_NOT_REGISTERED</code> to insert the booking form only if the user has not registered yet. Similar use <code>#_REMOVEBOOKINGFORM_IF_REGISTERED</code> to insert the booking removal form only if the user has already registered before. These two codes only work for WP users.'=>'<br>AnvûÊnd <code>#_ADDBOOKINGFORM_IF_NOT_REGISTERED</code> fûÑr att infoga bokningsformulûÊret bara om anvûÊndaren inte har registrerat sig ûÊnnu. AnvûÊnd liknande <code>#_REMOVEBOOKINGFORM_IF_REGISTERED</code> fûÑr att infoga borttagningsformulûÊret bara om anvûÊndaren redan har registrerat sig tidigare. Dessa tvûË koder fungerar bara fûÑr WP-anvûÊndare.','<br> Use <code>#_DIRECTIONS</code> to insert a form so people can ask directions to the event.'=>'<br> AnvûÊnd <code>#_DIRECTIONS</code> fûÑr att infoga ett formulûÊr sûË att personer kan be om vûÊgbeskrivning till evenemanget.','<br> Use <code>#_CATEGORIES</code> to insert a comma-separated list of categories an event is in.'=>'<br> AnvûÊnd <code>#_CATEGORIES</code> fûÑr att infoga en kommaseparerad lista ûÑver kategorier ett evenemang tillhûÑr.','<br> Use <code>#_ATTENDEES</code> to get a list of the names attending the event.'=>'<br> AnvûÊnd <code>#_ATTENDEES</code> fûÑr att fûË en lista ûÑver namnen pûË deltagarna i evenemanget.','Monthly period date format'=>'Datumformat fûÑr mûËnatlig period','The format of the date-string used when you use showperiod=monthly as an option to &#91;the eme_events] shortcode, also used for monthly pagination. Use php date() compatible settings.'=>'Format