nda OSA?','Check this option if you want to send emails for approved bookings.'=>'VûÊlj Ja om du vill sûÊnda e-post fûÑr godkûÊnda registreringar.','Enable paid RSVP emails?'=>'Aktivera e-post vid betald OSA?','Check this option if you want to send emails when a payment arrives via a payment gateway or when a booking is marked as paid.'=>'VûÊlj Ja om du vill om du vill sûÊnda e-post nûÊr betalning kommer in via en betalningslûÑsning eller nûÊr en bokning markeras som betald.','Send HTML emails'=>'Skicka HTML-formaterad e-post','Check this option if you want to use html in the emails being sent.'=>'VûÊlj Ja om du vill om du vill anvûÊnda html nûÊr du sûÊnder e-post.','Use mail queuing?'=>'AnvûÊnd e-postkûÑ?','If activated, you can plan emails for sending at a later date and time.'=>'Om aktiverat kan du planera e-postmeddelanden fûÑr sûÊndning vid senare datum och tid.','It is recommended to activate this option.'=>'Det rekommenderas att aktivera detta alternativ.','Email queue settings'=>'InstûÊllningar fûÑr e-postkûÑ','Send out queued emails in batches of '=>'SûÊnd kûÑad e-post i grupper om','Pause between emails'=>'Paus mellan e-postmeddelanden','Indicate how much time (in microseconds, one microsecond being one millionth of a second) to wait between queued emails being sent. By default this is 0, meaning EME sends emails in bursts based on your mail queue settings. This option can be used to send emails more slowly, but be aware to not cause PHP timeouts.'=>'Ange hur lûËng tid (i mikrosekunder, en mikrosekund ûÊr en miljarddel av en sekund) som ska vûÊntas mellan e-postmeddelanden i kûÑn. Som standard ûÊr detta 0, vilket innebûÊr att EME skickar e-post i burstar baserat pûË dina kûÑinstûÊllningar. Detta alternativ kan anvûÊndas fûÑr att skicka e-post lûËngsammare, men var uppmûÊrksam pûË att det inte orsakar PHP-tidsgrûÊnser.','Multisite data sharing is activated for EME, the option "%s" will use the settings from the main site'=>'Flerwebbplatsdelning av data ûÊr 