as och omdirigeringen sker omedelbart.','Default form format'=>'StandardformulûÊrformat','The default form format for submitting a new event.'=>'StandardformulûÊrformatet fûÑr att skicka in ett nytt evenemang.','Always show success message'=>'Visa alltid framgûËngsmeddelande','Check this option if you want to always show the success message even if the person submitting the event has the right to see the newly submitted event. This also means no redirection will happen.'=>'Markera detta alternativ om du alltid vill visa framgûËngsmeddelandet, ûÊven om personen som skickar in evenemanget har rûÊtt att se det nyss inskickade evenemanget. Detta innebûÊr ocksûË att ingen omdirigering kommer att ske.','The text shown to a guest when trying to submit a new event when they are not allowed to do so and the option to redirect to the login page is not set.'=>'Texten som visas fûÑr en gûÊst nûÊr de fûÑrsûÑker skicka in ett nytt evenemang nûÊr de inte har tillûËtelse att gûÑra det och alternativet att omdirigera till inloggningssidan inte ûÊr instûÊllt.','Check this option if you want the submitter to be redirected to the login page if not logged in (or does not have the needed access rights) and guests are not allowed to submit new events.'=>'Markera detta alternativ om du vill att den som skickar in ska omdirigeras till inloggningssidan om de inte ûÊr inloggade (eller inte har de nûÑdvûÊndiga behûÑrigheterna) och gûÊster inte har tillûËtelse att skicka in nya evenemang.','Access right to submit new events'=>'BehûÑrighet att skicka in nya evenemang','Inactive'=>'Inaktiv','Inactive memberships will not be shown in membership selection lists.'=>'Inaktiva medlemskap kommer inte att visas i medlemskapsvalslistor.','Payment success for your event submission'=>'Betalning lyckades fûÑr din evenemanginskickning','Payment failed for your event submission'=>'Betalning misslyckades fûÑr din evenemanginskickning','Event submit payment page'=>'Betalningssida fûÑr evenemanginskickning','Select a captcha to use'=>'VûÊlj en CAPTCHA att anvûÊnda','Frontend Draft (unpaid)'=>'Framsida-utkast (obetalt)','Basic EME Captcha'=>'GrundlûÊggande EME CAPTCHA','A new event has been submitted via the frontend'=>'Ett nytt evenemang har skickats in via framsidan','The following event has been submitted:<br>#_EVENTNAME (#_STARTDATE #_SARTTIME), edit it here: #_EDITEVENTLINK <br><br>Yours faithfully,<br>#_CONTACTPERSON'=>'FûÑljande evenemang har skickats in:<br>#_EVENTNAME (#_STARTDATE #_SARTTIME), redigera det hûÊr: #_EDITEVENTLINK <br><br>Med vûÊnlig hûÊlsning,<br>#_CONTACTPERSON','Check this option if you want to use hCaptcha on the booking/cancel/membership forms, to thwart spammers a bit. You can then either add #_CAPTCHA to your form layout yourself or it will automatically added just above the submit button if not present.'=>'Markera detta alternativ om du vill anvûÊnda hCaptcha pûË boknings-/avbryt-/medlemskapsformulûÊren fûÑr att motverka spammare lite. Du kan antingen lûÊgga till #_CAPTCHA i ditt formulûÊrlayout sjûÊlv eller sûË lûÊggs det automatiskt till ovanfûÑr skicka-knappen om det inte finns.','Check this option if you want to use Cloudflare Turnstile on the booking/cancel/membership forms, to thwart spammers a bit. You can then either add #_CAPTCHA to your form layout yourself or it will automatically added just above the submit button if not present.'=>'Markera detta alternativ om du vill anvûÊnda Cloudflare Turnstile pûË boknings-/avbryt-/medlemskapsformulûÊren fûÑr att motverka spammare lite. Du kan antingen lûÊgga till #_CAPTCHA i ditt formulûÊrlayout sjûÊlv eller sûË lûÊggs det automatiskt till ovanfûÑr skicka-knappen om det inte finns.','Frontend Event Submit Notification Email'=>'Aviserings-e-post fûÑr framsida-evenemanginskickning','Contact Person New Event Email Subject'=>'Kontaktperson nytt evenemang e-postûÊmne','The subject of the email that will be sent to the contact person when a new event is submitted.'=>'ûmnet fûÑr e-postmeddelandet som kommer att skickas till kontaktpersonen nûÊr ett nytt evenemang skickas in.','Contact Person New Event Email Body'=>'Kontaktperson nytt evenemang e-posttext','The body of the email that will be sent to the contact person when a new event is submitted.'=>'Texten fûÑr e-postmeddelandet som kommer att skickas till kontaktpersonen nûÊr ett nytt evenemang skickas in.','Author Payment Notification Email Subject'=>'FûÑrfattare betalningsavisering e-postûÊmne','The subject of the email that will be sent to the event author (the creator normally) when a payment notification is received via a payment gateway.'=>'ûmnet fûÑr e-postmeddelandet som kommer att skickas till evenemangets fûÑrfattare (skaparen normalt) nûÊr en betalningsavisering tas emot via en betalningsmetod.','Author Payment Notification Email Body'=>'FûÑrfattare betalningsavisering e-posttext','The body of the email that will be sent to the event author (the creator normally) when a payment notification is received via a payment gateway.'=>'Texten fûÑr e-postmeddelandet som kommer att skickas till evenemangets fûÑrfattare (skaparen normalt) nûÊr en betalningsavisering tas emot via en betalningsmetod.','Event paid mail attachments'=>'Betalda evenemang e-postbilagor','Optionally add attachments to the mail when an event is paid for.'=>'Valfritt: lûÊgg till bilagor till e-postmeddelandet nûÊr ett evenemang betalas.','Frontend Event Submit Payment form header format'=>'Framsida-evenemanginskickning betalningsformulûÊr rubrikformat','The format of the text shown above the payment buttons if the frontend submit form for events requires payment. If left empty, a default message will be shown.'=>'Formatet fûÑr texten som visas ovanfûÑr betalningsknapparna om framsida-inskickningsformulûÊret fûÑr evenemang krûÊver betalning. Om lûÊmnat tomt kommer ett standardmeddelande att visas.','Frontend Event Submit Payment form footer format'=>'Framsida-evenemanginskickning betalningsformulûÊr fotformat','The format of the text shown below the payment buttons if the frontend submit form for events requires payment.'=>'Formatet fûÑr texten som visas under betalningsknapparna om framsida-inskickningsformulûÊret fûÑr evenemang krûÊver betalning.','Also check out the \'Email templates\' and the \'Payment\' sections for some extra frontend submit settings.'=>'Kolla ocksûË in avsnitten \'E-postmallar\' och \'Betalning\' fûÑr extra instûÊllningar fûÑr framsida-inskickning.','Select the contact person that will receive email notifications whenever an event gets submitted or paid for. The mail templates are to be configured in the regular mail templates section.'=>'VûÊlj kontaktpersonen som kommer att fûË e-postaviseringar nûÊr ett evenemang skickas in eller betalas. E-postmallarna konfigureras i avsnittet fûÑr vanliga e-postmallar.','No contact'=>'Ingen kontakt','The message shown after successfully submitting a new event if the person submitting the event has no right to see the newly submitted event. The message is also shown if the event submission needs to be paid for and the redirection wait period (setting below this one) is not 0. This message can contain all event placeholders.'=>'Meddelandet som visas efter att ett nytt evenemang har skickats in framgûËngsrikt om personen som skickar in evenemanget inte har rûÊtt att se det nyss inskickade evenemanget. Meddelandet visas ocksûË om evenemanginskickningen behûÑver betalas och vûÊntetiden fûÑr omdirigering (instûÊllningen nedan denna) inte ûÊr 0. Detta meddelande kan innehûËlla alla evenemangsplatshûËllare.','No event found linked to this payment. If you believe you\'ve received this message in error please contact the site owner.'=>'Inget evenemang hittat kopplat till denna betalning. Om du tror att du fûËtt detta meddelande av misstag, vûÊnligen kontakta webbplatsûÊgaren.','Incorrect currency.'=>'Felaktig valuta.','The price to pay in order to submit a new event. Leave empty or 0 if no price is to be paid. This is not related to RSVP settings inside the submitted event itself! Configure the optional payment form header/footer sections in the EME Payment settings.'=>'Priset att betala fûÑr att skicka in ett nytt evenemang. LûÊmna tomt eller 0 om inget pris ska betalas. Detta ûÊr inte relaterat till RSVP-instûÊllningarna i det inskickade evenemanget! Konfigurera de valfria betalningsformulûÊrens rubrik-/fotavsnitten i EME BetalningsinstûÊllningarna.','The currency used when submitted events need to be paid for. This is not related to RSVP settings inside the submitted event itself!'=>'Valutan som anvûÊnds nûÊr inskickade evenemang behûÑver betalas. Detta ûÊr inte relaterat till RSVP-instûÊllningarna i det inskickade evenemanget!','The payment method(s) to be used when submitted events need to be paid for. This is not related to RSVP settings inside the submitted event itself!'=>'Betalningsmetoden/metoderna som ska anvûÊndas nûÊr inskickade evenemang behûÑver betalas. Detta ûÊr inte relaterat till RSVP-instûÊllningarna i det inskickade evenemanget!','Configured'=>'Konfigurerad','By default allow only one sign up for tasks per event for a person?'=>'TillûËt som standard bara en anmûÊlan fûÑr uppgifter per evenemang fûÑr en person?','Check this option if you want by default that a person can only signup for one task per event.'=>'Markera detta alternativ om du vill att en person som standard bara ska kunna anmûÊla sig till en uppgift per evenemang.','CSV delimiter'=>'CSV-avgrûÊnsare','Set the delimiter used in CSV exports.'=>'Ange avgrûÊnsaren som anvûÊnds i CSV-exporter.','Allow only one sign up for tasks per event for a person?'=>'TillûËt bara en anmûÊlan fûÑr uppgifter per evenemang fûÑr en person?','Only one signup allowed'=>'Bara en anmûÊlan tillûËten','Todos'=>'Att-gûÑra','Tasks can be used to rally volunteers to help with an event (e.g. 5 people behind the bar per shift, cleanup duty, ...) or to allow people to subscribe for a certain timeframe for an event (appointment-like). While you can impose limits and ask for confirmation for tasks, there is no price per task so no payment is possible upon subscribing for a task.'=>'Uppgifter kan anvûÊndas fûÑr att mobilisera frivilliga att hjûÊlpa till vid ett evenemang (t.ex. 5 personer bakom baren per skift, stûÊdtjûÊnst, ...) eller fûÑr att lûËta folk anmûÊla sig fûÑr en viss tidsram fûÑr ett evenemang (tidsbokningsliknande). ûven om du kan begrûÊnsa och bekrûÊfta uppgifter finns det inget pris per uppgift sûË ingen betalning ûÊr mûÑjlig vid anmûÊlan till en uppgift.','Enable todos for this event'=>'Aktivera att-gûÑra fûÑr detta evenemang','Each todo with a date in the past will send a mail to the contact person so you can use this to plan your event and not forget things. The date of the todo is based on the event start date and the todo offset parameter in days: an offset of 5 means 5 days before the event starts, an offset of -2 means 2 days after the event started.'=>'Varje att-gûÑra med ett datum i det fûÑrflutna kommer att skicka ett e-postmeddelande till kontaktpersonen sûË att du kan anvûÊnda detta fûÑr att planera ditt evenemang och inte glûÑmma saker. Datumet fûÑr att-gûÑra baseras pûË evenemangets startdatum och att-gûÑra-offsetparametern i dagar: ett offset pûË 5 betyder 5 dagar innan evenemanget bûÑrjar, ett offset pûË -2 betyder 2 dagar efter att evenemanget bûÑrjade.','List of todos'=>'Lista ûÑver att-gûÑra','Event start offset (days)'=>'Evenemangsstart-offset (dagar)','Add new todo'=>'LûÊgg till nytt att-gûÑra','Private events are only visible for logged in users. Draft events are not visible from the front end. Unlisted (hidden) events are not shown in any list or calendar. Frontend Draft is normally the state for events submitted via the frontend submit form.'=>'Privata evenemang ûÊr bara synliga fûÑr inloggade anvûÊndare. Utkast-evenemang ûÊr inte synliga frûËn framsidan. Olistade (dolda) evenemang visas inte i nûËgon lista eller kalender. Framsida-utkast ûÊr normalt statusen fûÑr evenemang som skickats in via framsida-inskickningsformulûÊret.','Unlisted (hidden)'=>'Olistat (dolt)','Send reminders for task signups'=>'Skicka pûËminnelser fûÑr uppgiftsanmûÊlningar','PDF mail attach format'=>'PDF e-postbilagsformat','When the template is being used as an attacment in a mail, the attachment has a default name. If you don\'t like the name given to the attachment in the mail, you can change it here. Relevant placeholders are allowed in their context (event/membership/booking/member/...). The \'.pdf\' extension will get added automatically, so no need to mention it.'=>'NûÊr mallen anvûÊnds som en bilaga i ett e-postmeddelande har bilagan ett standardnamn. Om du inte gillar namnet som ges till bilagan i e-postmeddelandet kan du ûÊndra det hûÊr. Relevanta platshûËllare ûÊr tillûËtna i sin kontext (evenemang/medlemskap/bokning/medlem/...). TillûÊgget \'.pdf\' lûÊggs till automatiskt, sûË det behûÑvs inte nûÊmnas.','Could not create the new location for this event: either you don\'t have the right to insert locations or there\'s a DB problem.'=>'Kunde inte skapa den nya platsen fûÑr detta evenemang: antingen har du inte rûÊttighet att infoga platser eller det finns ett databasproblem.','(opens in a new tab)'=>'(ûÑppnas en ny flik)','Attendees/bookings list ignore pending'=>'NûÊrvarande-/bokningslista ignorerar vûÊntande','Whether or not to ignore pending bookings when using the <code>#_ATTENDEES</code> or <code>#_BOOKINGS</code> placeholders.'=>'Huruvida vûÊntande bokningar ska ignoreras eller inte vid anvûÊndning av platshûËllarna <code>#_ATTENDEES</code> eller <code>#_BOOKINGS</code>.','Attendance PDF proof'=>'NûÊrvarobevis PDF','When the URL generated by #_ATTENDANCEPROOF_URL is visited, the selected PDF template will be used to generate a PDF for the user that can serve as proof of attendance. All event and RSVP placeholders are allowed.'=>'NûÊr URL:en som genereras av #_ATTENDANCEPROOF_URL besûÑks kommer den valda PDF-mallen att anvûÊndas fûÑr att generera en PDF